function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	-- delay a bit to give time for Vhenard VO get hit knockback exhertion to play a bit before Neyrelle's bark react
	Hydra.Wait(1);

	local boss = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "BOSS")
	for i, bossID in ipairs(boss) do
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convBark02, bossID); --Bark
	end
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	local boss = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "BOSS")
	
	for i, bossID in ipairs(boss) do
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convBark03, bossID); --Bark
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(2)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)
	if(Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idActorPlayer)) then
		--Boss Respawn Trigger Enabled
		Hydra.ActorEnable(BOSS_TRIGGER)
	else
		--Do nothing!
	end
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)
	--Reset Boss
	local boss = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "BOSS")
	for i, bossID in ipairs(boss) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(bossID)
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convBark01, bossID)
	end	
	--Manually Start Encounter
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(BOSS_LEVEL_AREA);
end
